    "AI can enhance these efforts through predictive analytics that identify at-risk individuals based on developmental, genetic, and environmental indicators.",
    "For example, AI has shown promising accuracy in detecting social determinants of health (Guevara et al., 2024).",
    "When integrated with EHR and lifestyle applications, AI systems can support personalized risk assessments and deliver tailored educational materials to families.",
    "At the population level, these tools can also design and deploy targeted public health campaigns.",
    "By enabling broader outreach and earlier detection -particularly in underserved communities, AI has the potential to significantly reduce disparities in communication health outcomes."
